      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:20:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世贸组织称中国工业补贴缺乏透明度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/wto-cites-lack-of-transparency-on-china-s-industrial-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界贸易组织强调中国在工业补贴方面“缺乏透明度”，暗示此类公开信息的缺乏引发了其他国家对中国商品充斥全球经济威胁的抱怨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/wto-cites-lack-of-transparency-on-china-s-industrial-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默在《国王的演讲》中撕毁了增长规划规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-rips-up-planning-rules-to-boost-growth-in-king-s-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 承诺将启动英国几十年来最雄心勃勃的规划改革，并表示推动国家建设是促进经济增长不可协商的一部分，同时他公布了以压倒性优势获胜的工党政府的立法议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-rips-up-planning-rules-to-boost-growth-in-king-s-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
